oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Walk the West at the Ace of Clubs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Boyd, Steve; Bull riding
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on split fountain, orange to green) Hatch poster announcing the pre-Memorial Day celebration featuring Walk in the West and A. K. A. Steve Boyd and Rich Park's new back at the Ace of Clubs. Poster features woodcut of bull and cowboy.
